                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-2383-18381022 t18381022-2383-punishment-119"></join>Confined Six Months</rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before Mr. Justice Williams</hi>.</p>
